»CL8:Proloque
»CL9:--------------------------------------
»CL7:Re-apperance trough the Gates of the
infinite Amiga screen window hooked up
to your mighty Amiga computer. Make
your imaginative brainwaves ready to
enter the virtual world of Amiga
Scene. The selective perception
towards the individual way of
receiving of what you call: 'The Amiga












Scene'. Don't keep your eyes shut!
Feel what's really happening. See the
bigger perspective... Realise the need
(towards yourself) of what we all know
as 'THE Amiga Scene..' Free your mind,
don't neglect your roots, keep it
going, yet in another priority.. 

»CL7:Welcome to the new Magical Moments
dear readers! With the 21st century
around the corner, this is one of the
best Magical Moment corner till date!
New is that fact that friends of mine
also can contribute. And this
time Alvin of ex-Generation fame who
recently joined Nah-kolor has
contributed with an fabulous article
about and with Rokdazone/Endzeit!


»CL8:Somebody Elses Lover..
