»CL7:Of course this is also the thirth time
in succesion that Magical Moments is
presented itself in the Official
Eurocharts! And we (Curt and I) hope
that there will be plenty more
occasions. This Magical Moments is
dedicated to Dreamer of Nah-kolor, who
recently surprised me with a
phone-call and a visit to my home,
here in good old Holland. Respect to
him, as we first meeted in August 1994
when we were still 'kids' ;)

Contrary to the popular believe also a
small 'thank you' to Dope and Infant
of Lemon. (or Spaceballs) fame, who
were so nice to send me a postcard
from Paris where they were on holiday
this summer.. 

There are times the scene tends to let
go of me, but luckily internet andmy
group(mates) let me hang in there.
Though the time I spend is really ata
minimum, this Magical Moments proves I
still got what it takes I suppose..
